{"tid":1387890,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"不要打狗，先溫馨攬實狗，等狗脫離唔到群眾嘅愛","createTime":"2019-07-30T15:23:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-30T15:29:23.000Z","uid":260988,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"78e44cfefe1d06c0285ba10e9fb601d3d3d7fd7a","tid":1387890,"uid":260988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T15:23:59.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">頭先見到有良民追打 popo<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"http://imgur.com/a/1XXJxuU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimgur.com%2Fa%2F1XXJxuU&d=RNMQoofY58y8BAaKNkwZNlgnvSLZGSqUYyTYHJNLWIM%3D&h=83e1b537\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://imgur.com/a/1XXJxuU</a><br />\n<br />\n這是不對的<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，既然我哋有咁多人，頭一兩個良民應該<span style=\"color: orange;\">迅速咁俾佢溫馨攬攬</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，咁佢就會融化喺抱抱之中，唔捨得走（或者走唔甩），其他人就更加可以好親切咁<span style=\"color: orange;\">蜂擁而上</span>，令佢感受<span style=\"color: red;\">民間熱情</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，可能從此身心被感化，以後選擇返做人</span><br />\n<br />\n應同請幫推<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30aca990edde365d95f5c2ecf967580b87c70020","tid":1387890,"uid":260988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T15:24:36.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"fbd1417ea8a0dc12f8afd12922716fc4f892fd9a","tid":1387890,"uid":260988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T15:24:49.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4de1785a5c6224e7133c3a42c7845023fff1f270","tid":1387890,"uid":260988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T15:25:00.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8a787e6eec7adb34664e94d2c528ef2c24e84a0c","tid":1387890,"uid":260988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T15:25:24.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"73a8db1d68fee48f